This directory is for project-specific libraries.

PlatformIO will install the following libraries automatically based on platformio.ini:

- Firebase Arduino Client Library for ESP8266 and ESP32
- MPU6050 library
- TinyGPSPlus
- ArduinoJson
- NTPClient
- EspSoftwareSerial

You can also add custom libraries to this directory if needed.

For more information about library management in PlatformIO:
https://docs.platformio.org/en/latest/librarymanager/